		<RichText x="962" y="287" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽甩出一枚雷珠，造成<span color="#ffacff">61%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="962" y="607" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽甩出一枚雷珠，造成<span color="#ffacff">150%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1634" y="287" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽抬头，在敌人处召唤落雷，造成<span color="#ffacff">142%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1634" y="607" width="380" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽永久提升<span color="#dfbfff">150元素精通</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="2306" y="287" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽抻直发令，所有友方灵蕈提升<span color="#ffbfbf">40%攻击力</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="2306" y="607" width="431" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽为场上的所有友方灵蕈施加「超限增幅」状态，灵蕈在攻击时将降下落雷，造成<span color="#ffacff">200%</span><span>伤害，该状态在12s后或触发4次后移除。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
