		<RichText x="377" y="853" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="233" height="36" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">Wt/Ed: 75/600</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#efbfff" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="397" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">3.5 灵蕈棋阵：<span color="#ffbfbf">150</span><span>元素精通。<br/>4.2 小小灵蕈大幻戏：</span><span color="#ffbfbf">100</span><span>元素精通，剧变反应系数1.5。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="962" y="927" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽甩出一枚雷珠，造成<span color="#ffacff">200%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1634" y="927" width="415" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽永久提升全队<span color="#dfbfff">80元素精通</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="2306" y="927" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">伸缩雷蕈兽为场上的所有友方灵蕈施加「超限」效果，「超限」下<span color="#ffb299">攻击力提升40%</span><span>，受伤时移除此效果。</span></p>
			</content>
